---

## On Session Start

At the start of every Silver Bullet workflow session, invoke the **`forge-session-init`** agent as a tool. It:

1. Detects the project's SB state (`.planning/PROJECT.md`, `STATE.md`, `ROADMAP.md`)
2. Loads the current phase, milestone, and required-skill list
3. Sets up session log and trivial-session marker
4. Returns a session summary with the next suggested action

If the project has no `.planning/` directory, run the `silver-init` skill first to scaffold it.

