| "how should we", "compare X vs Y", "spike", "investigate" | `silver-research` |
| "release", "publish", "version", "go live", "cut a release" | `silver-release` |
| "trivial", "quick fix", "typo", "one-liner", ≤3 files | `silver-fast` |
