| "where are we", "what's left", "show progress", "current status" | `gsd-progress` |
| "pick up", "resume", "continue where" | `gsd-resume-work` |
| "set up", "initialize", "install Silver Bullet" | `silver-init` |
| "quality review", "ilities" | `silver-quality-gates` |
