## Session Discipline

- Start each session: invoke `forge-session-init`
- During work: apply skills as the user requests / context implies
- Before commit: invoke `forge-pre-commit-audit` (and `forge-roadmap-freshness` if SUMMARY.md staged)
- After push: invoke `forge-ci-status-check`
- Before PR: invoke `forge-pre-pr-audit`, `forge-pr-traceability`, `forge-uat-gate` (for user-facing phases)
- Before declaring done: invoke `forge-task-complete-check`

