## Notes

- Forge auto-loads all skills from `~/forge/skills/`, `~/.agents/skills/`, and `.forge/skills/`. You don't need to "select" a skill — Forge picks based on context.
- Forge invokes custom agents from `~/forge/agents/` and `.forge/agents/` when their `id` is added to a calling agent's `tools[]` and `tool_supported: true` is set on the target.
- This file may be edited per-project to add project-specific routing or constraints. The forge-sb-install.sh installer will not overwrite an existing AGENTS.md.
